I am engaged to the greatest man in the world!! ❤️

When we started dating, it took just a few months to realise that you’re the one with whom I would want to spend the rest of my life with. For whom I can change countries and cities. You’re the one who will always keep me happy and protected. 

This feels surreal😌. 

Thank you my fiance for everything you do and for making my engagement dream come true. 

I love you today, tomorrow and forever❤️❤️. 

#engaged #myfiance #love
